      • signature

        java.lang.String signature()
        Returns a string describing the operations inside this query.

        For example, "sfpahol" means TableScan (s) followed by Filter (f) followed by Project (p) followed by Aggregate (a) followed by Filter (h) followed by Project (o) followed by Sort (l).

        See Also:
        isValidSignature(String)
